---
import DefaultLayout from '@layouts/DefaultLayout.astro'
---

<DefaultLayout title="About">
  <section class="about my-24">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="about-header">
        <h1>About</h1>
      </header>
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-content">
          <p>I'm a product manager with a technical background and 15+ years building for the web. I still love it.</p>
          <p>I studied Computer Engineering, then spent a decade building things for places like CERN, UCLA, AMC Networks, and various startups.</p>
          <p>In 2020 I joined <a href="https://versus.com/">Versus</a>, a comparison platform with 12 million monthly users. I figure out what needs to happen and make sure it doesâ€”product strategy, hiring, analyzing data, whatever the product needs. I like turning complex information into something people actually find useful.</p>
          <p>I'm a generalist by nature. I can go deep on data, prototype in code, run experiments, or zoom out to roadmaps.</p>
          <p>Based in Ourense, Spain. Remote since 2012.</p>
          <p>Got an interesting problem? <a href="mailto:fabio@fabiosouto.me">Let's talk</a>. Email works best, but I'm also on <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/fabiosouto">LinkedIn</a> and <a href="https://github.com/fasouto">Github</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="/avatar.png" alt="Fabio Souto illustration" width="500" height="600" />
          <span class="note">This is me (sort of)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>

<style>
  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    }
  }

  .about-content {
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .about-content a {
    color: #b85c38;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .about-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .about-image {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-image img {
      max-width: 200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  .note {
    font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #b85c38;
    display: block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    transform: rotate(-2deg);
  }
</style>
